description:
Leaked video: Border agents confront Biden's CBP chief for doing nothing to stop illegals at the border, a place, Clay notes, that they have most likely chosen for their "careers," not just stumbled into as a "job." Whoopi Goldberg doubles down on her Holocaust ignorance. Joy Behar wants more artists, especially young ones, to protest Spotify over Joe Rogan. The left's communist definition of "misinformation," including Buck's spot-on Russian pronunciation of a similar term.
